</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="734" pageNumber="735">
Liebherr (1991b) revised the species except for three Palaearctic species of the subgenus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bonelli" authorityYear="1810" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Anchomenus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="734" pageNumber="735" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="734" pageNumber="735">Anchomenus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
s.str.
</paragraph>
